node.text: She was a survivor who beat cancer twice.  She was inspirational but especially to female jurists.  Her journey and resilience gave us hope and strength to be relentless in the pursuit of justice.  She was our #SHERO our wonderful #Wonderwoman #Thankyou 🙏🏾#JusticeRuthBaderGinsburg #RGB #RIP #trailblazer ❣️👑⚖️

node.title: She broke ceilings.  She welcomed controversy, she fought for equality
